{"tid":2453392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[身曠心怡]日出康城被黨政府封樓","createTime":"2021-03-19T12:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T13:56:27.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e6318bf1d8bbd29619d7ac3c7d26f0cfde3604ab","tid":2453392,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3994825283936395/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3994825283936395%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=5bced0d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3994825283936395/</a><br />\n<br />\nStand News 立場新聞<br />\ntSp3hronisoredm  &middot;<br />\n政府再突襲封區，晚上 8 時起封鎖將軍澳日出康城領凱第 9 座，目標是在明日上午約 8 時左右完強制檢測。<br />\n<br />\n政府指，領凱第 9 座近期有確診個案，經評估後相關區域感染風險有機會較高，所以決定封區。<br />\n<br />\n現場直播：<a href=\"https://fb.watch/4kjk0J7Wuh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F4kjk0J7Wuh&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2BfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=6b9f18f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/4kjk0J7Wuh</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解唔封狗宿呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2d9251338de33f372b48380d5105b7417d5c0e","tid":2453392,"uid":292292,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"樓主，幾時移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523519546d8652d4df707438711ff233fcf9b92b","tid":2453392,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:42:06.000Z","msg":"達哥點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd0